OL,3,CMan, 60, admits strangling estranged
OL,4,Cwife at her home with bootlace
OL,6,FA 60-year-old man has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto murdering his estranged wife at her
OL,8,Fhome by wrapping a bootlace around her
OL,9,Fneck and strangling her.
OL,11,FRachel McDaid, 53, was killed by
OL,12,FMichael McDaid in the property in
OL,13,FNottingham Road, Eastwood, before her
OL,14,Fbody was discovered by one of her
OL,15,Fthree sons on April 19,
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Police said.
