OL,6,FMcDaid, of Acre Lane, Aston-on-Trent,
OL,7,FDerbyshire, pleaded guilty to the
OL,8,Foffence during an appearance at
OL,9,FNottingham Crown Court on Friday.
OL,11,F'I cannot even begin to comprehend the
OL,12,Fpain Rachel's loved ones were put
OL,13,Fthrough'
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Clare Dean,
OL,16,Fof the East Midlands Special
OL,17,FOperations Unit, said: "Michael
OL,18,FMcDaid's actions that day destroyed
OL,19,Fthe lives of the family members he was
OL,20,Fsupposed to care about the most.
