OL,6,F"I cannot even begin to comprehend the
OL,7,Fpain Rachel's loved ones were put
OL,8,Fthrough and what they will no doubt
OL,9,Fstill feel today because of his
OL,10,Fdespicable decision to murder his
OL,11,Fformer partner.
OL,13,F"Michael McDaid admitting what he did
OL,14,Fin court means the family will
OL,15,Fthankfully not now have to relive all
OL,16,Fthe details of the ordeal, which I
OL,17,Fhope provides them with some small
OL,18,Fdegree of comfort."
OL,20,FMcDaid is due to be sentenced next
OL,21,FFriday.
